- cs.MM (Multimedia): The title mentions "memoryless systems" which could be related to signal processing and multimedia systems. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing): The paper discusses the information loss in quantizers and limiters, which are commonly used in neural networks and other machine learning models.
